    "Pupils in this phase are in a pivotal juncture of their formative years, setting the foundations for their social competencies.",
    "This demographic requires ample avenues for group endeavors, facilitating an understanding and reverence for diverse viewpoints, while concurrently honing their communication acumen (Bocconi et al., 2018).",
